<div class="format_text" id="comment-body-18350">
<p>I think I could ditch my tv (I would still watch stuff at friends&#8217; houses sometimes), but my b/f is passionate about film.  And we live in a studio apartment&#8230;no walls between rooms!  My life is better with less watching anyway, and it&#8217;s better without a car.  I think I need to find really good activities to replace the tv time with, otherwise I&#8217;m afraid I&#8217;m &#8220;researching&#8221; on the internet too much.</p>
