<div class="format_text" id="comment-body-20979">
<p>I rarely watch T.V. anyhow, but I can&#8217;t really agree that it is simply no good for anything. There are so many things to be learned from everything! I generally only watch the History and Science Channels and I don&#8217;t necessarily find anything wrong with that&#8230; I mean, they present so much info that you just probably won&#8217;t find any where else! If only silly shows like most reality T.V. series were banned. I mean, T.V. really is the same as books, and very similar to the internet&#8230;</p>
