<p>People are always totally shocked by our lack of a TV set. We&#8217;ve had at least 3 friends offer us one, as if out lives aren&#8217;t complete without it. We watch the BBC online which is great as there are no ads, the program quality is exceptional and you simply can&#8217;t channel-hop, something which I used to spend most of my TV time doing!</p>
